MQuadExpr.getValue()

getValue ( )

Compute the value of a quadratic matrix expression using the current solution.

Return value:

Value of expression as an ndarary.

Example usage:

  qexpr = x @ A @ x
  model.addConstr(qexpr == 0)
  model.optimize()
  val = qexpr.getValue()
